description:
See for yourself how natural healing can prevent and reverse killer diseases. Learn the true nature of disease processes, discover how nutrition can affect mental health, and explore the remarkable field of orthomolecular medicine in this informative lecture. Raymond Obomsawin shares some of the harmful and deceptive practices in modern medicine. He reveals alarming statistics that show that modern medical practices have a direct correlation with increase of death rates. Learn about the vast difference in effectiveness between modern medicine and natural healing.
